TextChange: What is success?  Although success has a general definition of an acheivment or accomplishment, that doesn't mean everyone views success the same.  What may be successful to one person, someone else might not consider that a success.  Success can vary greatly depeding on many different aspects.  So if one was to question if people acheieve more success by cooperation or by competition could go both ways depending on the circumstances per the individual, and also depending on if the term \"people\" in this prompt is viewing people as each indiviual or people together as a whole.
